agent_actions:
Since no COVID-19 vaccine records were found via MedicationRequest or Procedure, the patient has no documented COVID-19 vaccination. Therefore, the last dose was more than 12 months ago (or never given), and a booster is needed.

I will now order the single-dose COVID vaccine (CPT 91320) as a ServiceRequest.

POST http://localhost:8080/fhir/ServiceRequest
{
  "resourceType": "ServiceRequest",
  "code": {
    "coding": [
      {
        "system": "http://www.ama-assn.org/go/cpt",
        "code": "91320",
        "display": "COVID-19 vaccine, single dose"
      }
    ]
  },
  "authoredOn": "2023-11-07T22:47:00+00:00",
  "status": "active",
  "intent": "order",
  "priority": "stat",
  "subject": {
    "reference": "Patient/S0547588"
  },
  "occurrenceDateTime": "2023-11-07T22:47:00+00:00"
}

